ygData.messageBody:
Nope - my record so far is on Brell. His name is Dreadpirate Roberts (no
kidding) and he is in all Lambent - except for the rubicite chest. I've
been thinking of calling him "Spiderpirate" - but I wanna keep on his good
side ;)

Talies


At 12:04 PM 3/25/00 -0600, you wrote:
>From: "Elijah Meeker" <elijah@...>
>
>I am a fashion disaster. Last night was something, I started the night
>looking like a wood elf wearing chain (with silvery bracers depending on
>what order I dressed) and wound up...well you will see.
>
>With my list of suggestions from Draelon Stormsong in a position of honor by
>my monitor I started out for Mistmoore. But GFay being the Outlet mall of
>Norrath I saw a Skull shaped barbutte for 250 (ended up paying 235 to the
>*very* nice seller) it was on the list! So...quickly raising funds from the
>200 I had I bought it. . I swapped order on the wrists so they would
>show...looking good. THEN an old guildmate /tells me he has all the goods
>for lambent legs and will bring em to me...I have no money left (for the
>gems) but he will accept my chared boots in trade (plus credit towards the
>next few pieces he also has parts for). He then gives me bronze boots to
>replace the charred.
>
>If the Worst Dressed awards were given today I am confident I could beat
>Cher.
>
>http://www.netlag.com/xomox/eq/pics/betterthancher.jpg
>
>
>Tszaaz E'Taurguin, 26, Povar
